high_descs: Turn around and go to the door and turn right, then go across the room to the counter ahead of you.
Pick up the butter knife on the far right side of the counter top.
Turn around and towards the kitchen island to your right.
Cut the bread near the edge of the island into slices.
Turn around towards the refrigerator.
Place the butter knife on the front of the top shelf of the refrigerator.
Turn back around to the bread that was just cut, on the kitchen island.
Pick up one of the bread slices from the island.
Turn to your right and step forward into the walk way, then turn to your left and go to the microwave across from you.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator on the other side of the island.
Place the slice of bread on the top shelf of the refrigerator, behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a warm slice of bread in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around, go halfway across the room, turn right and go to the counter across the room.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and go to the counter in the middle of the room.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf in the fridge.
Turn around to the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go right and then turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn around, go across the room and go to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread on the top shelf with the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left to face the center table.
Cut the bread on the table into slices.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around to face the bread on the center table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat the potato and place it in the fridge.
